'''Noori Gate''' is a historical landmark, located in [[Sargodha]], [[Punjab, Pakistan|Punjab]], [[Pakistan]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.google.com/maps/place/Noori+Gate/@32.0842199,72.6603341,15z/data=!4m5!3m4!1s0x0:0xf0f71530ca661b8!8m2!3d32.0842199!4d72.6603341 |title=Google Maps |website=Google.com |date= |accessdate=2016-09-16}}</ref> Noori Gate was built during [[British Empire|British Colonial Era]] in 1903.

